  "title": "Quantity Surveyor/ Senior Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job summary:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Permanent role</p></li><li><p>Basic Up to $5,500</p></li><li><p>5.5 days (Alternate Saturday)</p></li><li><p>Working location at West</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job scope:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Handle measurements, costing tasks, and verification of contractors’ work claims, including preparing progress payments and managing additional/omission works.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with the Client on documentation matters, including submitting cost-related reports and finalizing accounts/claims.</p></li><li><p>Maintain proper project documentation such as drawings, records, and cost updates throughout the project cycle.</p></li><li><p>Track and document any changes to scope, adjustments, or variations that arise during construction.</p></li><li><p>Support the project team with any other duties or administrative tasks as required.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li><p>Strong ability to interpret drawings, specifications, and technical documents.</p></li><li><p>Skilled in contract administration, VO handling, and negotiating commercial terms.</p></li><li><p>Independent, detail-focused, analytical, proactive, and capable of working under tight timelines while collaborating well with others.</p></li><li><p>Role is based on-site at the project office.<br /></p><p>Please submit your updated resume by using the</p><p><strong>APPLY NOW BUTTON</strong></p><p>By submitting your personal data and/or resume to us in connection with your job application, you will be deemed to have agreed and consented to us in collecting, using, retaining, and disclosing your personal data and/or resume to prospective employers for the purpose of the evaluating, processing and administration by company relating to this job application.</p><p>*We regret to inform you that only shortlisted candidates would be notified* We wish you all the best in your career search.</p><p>You are welcome to visit our website at http://www.rkgroup.sg/<br /></p><p>RK Recruitment Pte Ltd | EA License No.: 20C0280<br />Raymond Ng Jun Han | EA Personnel No.: R1657009</p></li></ul>",
